Class DataFileAvroStore<K,T extends PersistentBase>

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, DataStore<K,T>, FileBackedDataStore<K,T>, org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configurable, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable

    public class DataFileAvroStore<K,T extends PersistentBase>
extends AvroStore<K,T>
    DataFileAvroStore is file based store which uses Avro's DataFile{Writer,Reader}'s as a backend. This datastore supports mapreduce.
